SEARCH
Package grafioschtrader.repository

Interface HoldCashaccountBalanceJpaRepository.CashaccountBalanceChangeTransaction

Enclosing interface:
HoldCashaccountBalanceJpaRepository
public static interface HoldCashaccountBalanceJpaRepository.CashaccountBalanceChangeTransaction
Projection interface representing daily aggregated cash account balance changes.

Populated by native queries that sum various transaction types per cash account and date:

  • withdrawal/deposit (WITHDRAWAL, DEPOSIT)
  • interest (INTEREST_CASHACCOUNT)
  • fees (FEE)
  • accumulate/reduce (ACCUMULATE, REDUCE)
  • dividends (DIVIDEND)
  • total net change
Also provides portfolio context and currency codes.
